Print the vector and find the min and max elements.When run with the input3 8 5 2 3 7 -1, the program should produce the following output:Enter numbers to add (use -1 to stop): 3 8 5 2 3 7 -1
With array ( 3, 8, 5, 2, 3, 7 ):
